Description: bistory
        =======
        
        A small python application that implements bash history searching in
        your terminal
        
        |image0|
        
        Installation
        ------------
        
        ::
        
            $ pip install --user bistory
        
        Configuration
        -------------
        
        .bash_profile
        ~~~~~~~~~~~~~
        
        ::
        
            if [[ $- =~ .*i.* ]]; then
                bind '"\C-r": "\C-a bistory \C-j"'
            fi
        
